articles.author: Aidan Lewis, Nafisa Eltahir
articles.title: Cairo Peace Summit ends without Gaza breakthrough - Reuters
articles.description: Arab leaders at a Cairo summit on Saturday condemned Israeli bombardment of Gaza as Europeans said civilians should be shielded, but with Israel and senior U.S. officials absent there was no agreement towards containing the violence.
